init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This is a very bad time for dads.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The government decides to make a new law that says that all dads have to be ranked.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The government hears the uproar and decides to repeal the law.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The rankings are removed and all of the dads are happy.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The government is now seen as the enemy and they will do anything to get back at them.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The government is now in a tough situation.
